				<wikidot:authorName>contravariant</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2416023</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't see how being a gross human parasite with a weird life cycle warrants an SCP classification, though. It's neither anomalous nor an existential threat. If the Foundation was in that business, I imagine they would classify the Guinea worm and the human botfly as well.</p> 
				 	]]>
